#

Crispy Baked Falafel with Tahini Sauce and Roasted Vegetable Salad

$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

Sesame

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

VeganHealthyGluten-Free

Description

Deliciously crispy falafel paired with a creamy tahini sauce and a vibrant roasted vegetable salad, perfect for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • Garlic: 3 cloves
  • Cilantro: 1/2 cup
  • Parsley: 1/2 cup
  • Ground Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Ground Coriander: 1 tsp
  • Baking Powder: 1 tsp
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Tahini: 1/4 cup
  • Lemon Juice: 2 tbsp
  • Roasted Vegetables (e.g., bell peppers, zucchini, carrots): 4 cups
